Available Stocks
The program currently supports the following stocks:
Stock Symbol	Price ($)
AAPL	180
TSLA	250
GOOGL	140
AMZN	130
MSFT	320
You can easily add more stocks by updating the stock_prices dictionary.
How to Run
Install Python 3 on your system.
Save the code as stock_tracker.py.
Open a terminal or command prompt.
Run the program:
python stock_tracker.py
